{"tid":2332370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"綁劫網紅蘇淼淼案，被告包括地產經紀家庭主婦","createTime":"2020-12-19T14:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T15:07:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"67af93cee69a79c4bf8d613c2aa17d098c12c6c6","tid":2332370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/m.G0Q.0b9LMiT0Eb7Bt.0w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Bs6xlXnES80Vy61XaKcSvw--~B/aD03NTA7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/singtao.com.hk/ea342944cbb39516464de97ff2179a77\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fm.G0Q.0b9LMiT0Eb7Bt.0w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBs6xlXnES80Vy61XaKcSvw--~B%2FaD03NTA7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsingtao.com.hk%2Fea342944cbb39516464de97ff2179a77&h=e18751b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】現年25歲的女網紅蘇淼淼（CRY SO）在11月24日早上，遭3名手持生果刀的男賊人闖入位於荔枝角的豪宅寓所，3人襲擊並綁起蘇淼淼、蘇的6個月大兒子及女傭，搶劫市值超過1100萬的名表、電子產品、名牌手袋及手飾後逃去。3男被控一項搶劫罪，其中一男的妻子則被控一項處理贓物罪。羅德泉主任裁判官把案件押後至明年2月1日再訊，以待警方進一步調查，持雙程證的女被告獲准以現金5000元擔保外出侯訊。<br />\n<br />\n39歲地盤工人陳少達、39歲無業漢梁旭賢、39歲地產經紀黎景安，被控於2020年11月24日，在深水埗荔枝角道873號「一號．西九龍」某單位，搶劫蘇美欣，劫去一個行李箱、21個手袋、8隻手表、14件珠寶首飾、一個卡片套、一部手提電話、一部手提電腦、一件外套、港幣8萬元現金，共值1180.6萬元。<br />\n<br />\n3男另被控於同日同地搶劫女傭Baisto Benigna Neseo，並劫去一部手提電話及港幣8000元現金，總值港幣1萬元。31歲家庭主婦李洋被控於2020年12月17日，在九龍慈雲山毓華街慈康邨康秀樓某單位，知道或相信某些物品是贓物，而該等贓物，即3個總值21500元並屬於蘇美欣的手袋，但仍然不誠實地從事或協助另一人，或為另一人的利益，而將贓物保留、搬遷、處置、變現。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，首被告陳少達與女被告李洋為夫妻關係，而原名為蘇美欣的女網紅蘇淼淼，與女傭及6個月大兒子在涉案單位居住了3個月，首被告陳少達及次被告梁旭賢，與另一名在逃男子，涉嫌在案發當日手持生果刀衝入單位，綁起3名事主後搶掠涉案財物並放入行李箱。"},{"pid":"141dd6d7ccd93e0a5fbbfcb835ac87787690d7a7","tid":2332370,"uid":321977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"其實呢條女有咩新聞/討論價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6be2ee19cef11c72dbbff8afc621c730496ca4","tid":2332370,"uid":171786,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"141dd6d7ccd93e0a5fbbfcb835ac87787690d7a7","tid":2332370,"uid":321977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"其實呢條女有咩新聞/討論價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:28:24.000Z","msg":"關咩條女事，個新聞價值係上門老笠呀，係你自己將個價值shift去條女度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60bda0a2b43c68ecb2694c54976ec48b579ef83","tid":2332370,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:33:11.000Z","msg":"條女點解會咁有錢？"},{"pid":"ead122076049fadb3d5a51f70a0140d551fad054","tid":2332370,"uid":263183,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fm.G0Q.0b9LMiT0Eb7Bt.0w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBs6xlXnES80Vy61XaKcSvw--~B%2FaD03NTA7dz0xMDAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsingtao.com.hk%2Fea342944cbb39516464de97ff2179a77&amp;h=e18751b4&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n真係S級封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43434b81bfce8dc83803f37dfb1480d15e58f239","tid":2332370,"uid":159870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ead122076049fadb3d5a51f70a0140d551fad054","tid":2332370,"uid":263183,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fm.G0Q.0b9LMiT0Eb7Bt.0w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FB